<p>
  <span class="nym">Cleopas</span>
  <span class="gen">m.</span>
  
  <span class="etym"><span class="lang">Ancient Greek</span> <i>κλέος</i> '(good) report; flame, glory' + <span class="lang">Ancient Greek</span> <i>πατήρ</i> 'father'.
  </span>
  
</p>
  
<div class="usg">
  <p>The name of a 1st C saint and apostle. Wycliffite Bible (1395): <i>Cleofas</i>.</p>
</div>
  
  


